      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "With this we got another capability because real development was done in Maths that some scientist \ncome up with some good maths formula.\nEven for Machine Learning and AI to exist vectors were always there but there was even a way to store\nthese vectors in database. But there are so many vecotrs and vectors we store in a bigger level it\nbecomes more like a 3D model",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "With this we got another capability because real development was done in Maths that some scientist \ncome up with some good maths formula.\nEven for Machine Learning and AI to exist vectors were always there but there was even a way to store\nthese vectors in database. But there are so many vecotrs and vectors we store in a bigger level it\nbecomes more like a 3D model",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
