    {
      "id": "yZbxT71eXiQ5WcTCF0BJw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2186.3848922125817,
      "y": 10963.092980211251,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bHQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1515524723,
      "version": 1042,
      "versionNonce": 1651384668,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775577067459,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Replicate Human Behaviour. there is no other purpose of AI apart from replicating Human \nbehaviour.\nFor example -> Automation means code that we are doing, but now our machine will do that is automation.\nMachine Learning is Classify & Prediction that we do by our eyes, by our thinking, by our logic, we classify\ncertain things and we predict what can happen next.\nNLP -> we obviously we can recognize this is a pen that is Natural language processing. Or Image processing or\n    Video processing or anything like that.\nDeep Learning -> If we can see a very blur cat but still identify it is a cat that is deep learning.\nLLM -> LLMs are trying to talk that is what we do.\n\nHere also by building Agents what we are trying to do is that, LLM will give some textual output, and\nnow we are building a tool on top of that and tool takes certain actions.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Replicate Human Behaviour. there is no other purpose of AI apart from replicating Human \nbehaviour.\nFor example -> Automation means code that we are doing, but now our machine will do that is automation.\nMachine Learning is Classify & Prediction that we do by our eyes, by our thinking, by our logic, we classify\ncertain things and we predict what can happen next.\nNLP -> we obviously we can recognize this is a pen that is Natural language processing. Or Image processing or\n    Video processing or anything like that.\nDeep Learning -> If we can see a very blur cat but still identify it is a cat that is deep learning.\nLLM -> LLMs are trying to talk that is what we do.\n\nHere also by building Agents what we are trying to do is that, LLM will give some textual output, and\nnow we are building a tool on top of that and tool takes certain actions.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UDrTRjvxh7g2u0sSUiQeZ",
      "type": "text",
